Welcome to the Yu-Gi-Oh! Wikia! 
The Yu-Gi-Oh! Wikia is a free repository on all aspects of the Yu-Gi-Oh! franchise that anyone can edit. We've been around since May 26, 2005 — and in that time we've assembled a lot of information about the cards and other aspects of the Yu-Gi-Oh! phenomenon. Please click here for dates of upcoming Yu-Gi-Oh! TCG & OCG product releases, as well as anime air dates and manga book release dates. Characters 
There are a lot of characters in this long-running franchise. Here are some of the characters from the upcoming film, Yu-Gi-Oh! The Dark Side of Dimensions .
